This repository contains scripts and data for reproducing results for following paper:
Bleka et al (2016): Improved deconvolution of sequenced based mixtures by extending EuroForMix


The folder contains the organised system to perform following:

1) Calculations: Excecute RUNCALCULATIONS.R
	- Performs MAE estimation and Deconvolution
	
2) Comparisons: Excecute RUNCOMPARE.R
	- Performs comparison between true contributing reference profiles and 
	deconvolved profiles (aligning profiles).
	- Creates performance-metrics for the aligned profiles (Brier, accuracy, etc )
	- Creates result tables showing performance (study-wise)

3) Summary: Excecute RUNCREATESUMMARY.R
	- Creates tables and figures for summarizing results across studies
	- Also creates some of the supplementary results

4) Supplementary Analyses: Excecute RUNSUPPLEMENTARY.R
	- Creates tables and figures for summarizing results for supplementary (MPS-STR dataset)
	

Other:
5) Checking reference-evidence overlap: Excecute CHECK_REFEVID_OVERLAP